symbols.description:
Renders type names for diagnostic overlays.

Example:
---
struct Sprite { enum renderName = "sprite"; }
assert(renderLabel(Sprite.init) == "sprite");
---

Template mixin-style system runner.

Examples:
---
auto out = runSystem!TickSystem(3);
assert(out == 6);
---

Returns a boxed value.

Examples:
---
auto b = makeBox!int(9);
